description: When Ben left Ellington's band in the summer of 1943, he quickly became an in-demand recording artist, on top of co-leading a quartet with drummer Big Sid Catlett.
title: The Sound of Ben Webster: Part Four
fulltitle: The Sound of Ben Webster: Part Four
